<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica"><BR>     Other than whats already been mentioned, I love my 54 spell Blizzard.  Its a 1470 damage 3 wave AoE, and fits in quite nicely when you know when to use it.  I don't use it when multiple mobs are present, or when I'm in a confined space where it would hit me too.  I cast it when the MoB hits about 3/4 health, and about 70% of the time it hits for full damage.  IMO it is pretty efficient, and gives you a good feeling when you hit for full.  It's also great if you happen to be in one of those rare wacko groups that like to AoE, but usually I prefer to stay away from those <IMG SRC="/boards/images/smiles/icon_smile.gif"></FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#e6ebd7"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=1282"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Malivolta"></a>
